        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Geniuses\\' existence does not bother many people, but their downfalls are undoubtedly the most captivating gossip.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 5,
        "ActionId": 5,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Due to using M.I.N.D. connections so intensely to the point of self-harm, he suffered incurable mental damages that disqualified him from forever being a commandant, and he instead volunteered to be a Construct.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 6,
        "ActionId": 6,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: '—Everyone will hear about this story one way or the other, even without actively searching for it.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 7,
        "ActionId": 7,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'F.O.S. Military Command College is meant to cultivate commandants that can command Constructs. Instead, he has ended up as a chess piece to be commanded.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Although his specialized Inver-Device means that he does not have to be bonded to a commandant, just being a Construct is enough to cast Chrome in a narrative he cannot alter.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'To allow a Construct on a stage to speak as an alumnus...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'To some people, this is as offensive as a subordinate ordering his superiors around.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Even when this Construct was once a Chief of F.O.S.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'That is all in the past now.'}"
    },
